column1: Notes:
DO NOT ADD/DELETE/MOVE ANY COLUMNS OR ROWS
This is the New_Calculations sheet
which replaces the old Calculations sheet.
You probably can't see any formulas on here
UPDATE 7-15-21: TimeTrialsStats were just added, and are
calculated manually with pure spreadsheet formulas because I
don't want to bother automating it at the moment
Thats because this sheet is filled in using
a Google Apps Script File (Tools > Script Editor).
DO NOT CHANGE ANYTHING IN THERE WITHOUT PERMISSION!
The old Calculations sheet is still around
but it is hidden since it no longer serves a
purpose and is/was an unmaintainable mess
and a complete pain in the üçë to update
whenever a new tank or gamemode was added.
This New_Calculations sheet on the other hand
should (lotionfully) automatically adjust itself
whenever new tanks and gamemodes are added
and continue working as intended without breaking.
The script is made such that the player/tank stats
will be printed as a table starting from a specific
cell (currently F3 and M3). You can change these
cells and some other stuff at the top of the code.
The old Calculations sheet will still be kept
around as a backup just in case New_Calculations
ends up not working out for whatever reason. Also,
the old Player/Tank Stats formulas are availiable
as notes in Calculations"
